{"tid":1761449,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"岑子杰：證林鄭為緊急法試水溫","createTime":"2019-11-29T02:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T03:55:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"071620f8f4e912e4eb77b7cbe4d1390571c87b1b","tid":1761449,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191129/5VUS5LUSNHR4EJQHDKQNRI6VYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191129%2F5VUS5LUSNHR4EJQHDKQNRI6VYU%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLYhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=640bcd9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191129%2F5VUS5LUSNHR4EJQHDKQNRI6VYU%2F&h=77131ddd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191129/5VUS5LUSNHR4EJQHDKQNRI6VYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n岑子杰：證林鄭為緊急法試水溫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191129/large/1574959523_266e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191129%2Flarge%2F1574959523_266e.jpg&h=361a7733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑子杰<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】蒙面法借屍還魂，民陣召集人岑子杰質疑，警方在現行法例下已有權力要求受查人士除下面罩，核實身份，但特首仍繞過立法程序通過蒙面法，證明立法是為緊急法試水溫，做法可悲及可恥。保安局否認，稱立法是協助警方執法，並無其他目的。<br />\n<br />\n高院上周一裁定蒙面法違憲，警方見招拆招，改以其他現行法例阻止示威者蒙面。岑子杰表示，警方內部通告證明一直有法例可以達到同樣效果，反映立蒙面法沒有需要，「原來你係有權力，點解仲要亂立一條法例，禁止人去蒙面，更加冇道理」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒料縱容濫暴<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美跨黨派讚好：捍衞勇敢港人<br />\n<br />\n岑質疑，林鄭月娥繞過立法會既有程序立法，只為動用緊急法試水溫，擴大其無上權力，做法可悲及可恥。他要求政府立即撤回蒙面法的上訴，人大亦不應以釋法干預香港三權分立。他指林鄭如不解決政治問題，任何打壓和平遊行集會的方法，只會適得其反。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員區諾軒認為，警方鑽法律空子，挑釁市民，其實捉錯用神，以為增加執法權力可以提高執法效率，但濫捕濫告嚴重，令群眾反抗。他又擔心，蒙面法實施後，警方在街上阻嚇市民，隨便移除路人面罩，擔心通告發出後，警方繼續縱容濫暴，激化市民情緒。<br />\n<br />\n保安局回覆指，訂立蒙面法是為加強對激進示威者在隱藏身份的情況下進行非法及暴力行為的阻嚇力，協助警方執法，並無其他目的，強調特首會同行政會議是基於當前危害公安的情況，以《緊急情況規例條例》立法，有別於目前本港其他法例。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾偉龍"},{"pid":"15a35f3035715ac92e296fb62c163e06fc4afbfa","tid":1761449,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:44:30.000Z","msg":"1130 中學生銀髮集會 12.1 中環遊行 尖沙咀遊行 12.8民陣集會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6Y6vgF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6Y6vgF.jpg&h=fbb1f935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rs8eD91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frs8eD91.jpg&h=36832b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCEQWWH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCEQWWH.jpg&h=7ad7d7b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3dc5b83b847cf19b08594352218dba926e43e1b","tid":1761449,"uid":281020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"屌你蘋果照妖鏡<br />\n影到岑子杰咁柒"},{"pid":"f301c4572a6a8a390f759385397cda7c578397ab","tid":1761449,"uid":316537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"好似整容咁"},{"pid":"4bfe3a7876ee14d5fb719718ad59f00f372da669","tid":1761449,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解焦點去左個圖度"},{"pid":"3a5a5aca94d1a144129303e3b6fc4b9fe31a8b00","tid":1761449,"uid":77788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccfcc87c750d1cf81896c986ce50459e94ed1451","tid":1761449,"uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:55:35.000Z","msg":"張圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cls"}]}